ce of cloth like the fillet upon the round of her head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"leaving the crown uncovered]. (Mgh and L and Msb voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miEojarN","text_ar":"مِعْجَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  See also 1, in six places. ―         -b3-  And see 4."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}